><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634706\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人-300x226.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"377\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人-300x226.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人-1024x772.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人-768x579.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人-1080x815.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/突然大家都成了诗人.png 1368w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634708\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵-300x73.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"122\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵-300x73.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵-1024x250.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵-768x188.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵-1080x264.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/诗朗诵.png 1368w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634709\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗-300x139.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"231\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗-300x139.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗-1024x474.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗-768x355.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗-1080x500.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/拼接诗.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-634724\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/005tIVgCgy1gblmmftqypj30rs0ox4qp-300x269.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://c